# Grimverse State Propagation Rule

When a shot or event becomes canon:
- record the new delta
- update scarring_log
- update forbidden_drift
- update physical_state / mental_state if changed
- keep the previous baseline visible
- create a state delta note if one does not yet exist

## Rule
Never mutate state without an explicit canon trigger.

## Required output when a winner is promoted
- the delta summary
- the affected state node
- the next scene impact
